{"tid":2478384,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"消息：拜登會延續特朗普政策  重新興建圍牆","createTime":"2021-04-07T04:27:26.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-07T04:49:34.000Z","uid":227801,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"cfca1c48d14661247b70a5dda84db8886dbb8108","tid":2478384,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T04:27:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-9441641/Biden-wants-RESTART-construction-Trumps-border-wall-plug-gaps-DHS-head-Mayorkas-says.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dailymail.co.uk%2Fnews%2Farticle-9441641%2FBiden-wants-RESTART-construction-Trumps-border-wall-plug-gaps-DHS-head-Mayorkas-says.html&d=8bD6%2Ff4xTvH2AAK2Q7vPtJktsUQkmpJZziL8xq2DbDY%3D&h=19c6f889\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-9441641/Biden-wants-RESTART-construction-Trumps-border-wall-plug-gaps-DHS-head-Mayorkas-says.html</a><br />\nJoe Biden&nbsp;is considering restarting construction on&nbsp;Donald Trump's southern border wall as his administration continues to grapple with a growing&nbsp;immigration&nbsp;crisis including record numbers of illegal crossers.<br />\nHomeland Security Secretary Alejandro Mayorkas told employees, according to the&nbsp;Washington Times, that construction might resume to plug 'gaps' in the current barrier between the U.S. and Mexico.<br />\n<br />\n&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/americas/us-politics/dhs-alejandro-mayorkas-border-wall-b1827535.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.independent.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Famericas%2Fus-politics%2Fdhs-alejandro-mayorkas-border-wall-b1827535.html&d=8bD6%2Ff4xTvH2AAK2Q7vPtJktsUQkmpJZziL8xq2DbDY%3D&h=03873830\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/americas/us-politics/dhs-alejandro-mayorkas-border-wall-b1827535.html</a><br />\nConstruction on&nbsp;Donald Trump's&nbsp;border wall&nbsp;may continue under&nbsp;Joe Biden's administration, reports suggest.<br />\nDepartment of Homeland Security&nbsp;Secretary&nbsp;Alejandro Mayorkas&nbsp;told department employees that he may be green-lighting work on the wall to plug &quot;gaps&quot; in the current wall."},{"pid":"8f078915861f3a42e2e1bf15d3ea0d350ae47b12","tid":2478384,"uid":156542,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T04:28:14.000Z","msg":"呢條友好垃圾 <br />\n左膠出嚟講嘢未"},{"pid":"cef52b5e43e93f80d959ca12e405c3ad96dffc2e","tid":2478384,"uid":70487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T04:29:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sleep.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />sleepy"},{"pid":"8bc5ebef1cc9df31f577514228d2251052ea1794","tid":2478384,"uid":32782,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T04:29:50.000Z","msg":"乜柒都無做 淨係拎trump d前朝政績"},{"pid":"53bc06ae884e46fd981d2b7e3dd40d8a79bd533e","tid":2478384,"uid":227801,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8f078915861f3a42e2e1bf15d3ea0d350ae47b12","tid":2478384,"uid":156542,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T04:28:14.000Z","msg":"呢條友好垃圾 <br />\n左膠出嚟講嘢未"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T04:30:00.000Z","msg":"我唔會選擇怨婦式 熱狗式諗野， 佢肯跟返嚟好囉"},{"pid":"954f67b3126c7d3235b846cf98164afe1eee9d69","tid":2478384,"uid":227801,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"8bc5ebef1cc9df31f577514228d2251052ea1794","tid":2478384,"uid":32782,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T04:29:50.000Z","msg":"乜柒都無做 淨係拎trump d前朝政績"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T04:30:55.000Z","msg":"咁咪好囉， 佢肯跟返 唔通你想佢唔跟<br />\n千祈唔好做熱狗式怨婦"},{"pid":"78c5fcbdf076c883f3b80bc8d9e0a7494443673d","tid":2478384,"uid":310275,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T04:31:55.000Z","msg":"愛侵力：我睇唔到，仲之拜登一定係奶共9up<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sleep.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/ass